sentence for her murder.

11:51.291 --> 11:53.417
Because smoking kills!

11:53.458 --> 11:55.375
How's that for cool.

11:55.417 --> 11:57.583
-Oh my God.

11:57.625 --> 11:59.834
That's so awful.

11:59.875 --> 12:03.083
We're completely stunned.

12:03.125 --> 12:05.125
[Girls laugh]

12:05.166 --> 12:07.333
