fall for that.

12:07.375 --> 12:10.583
[Girls laugh]
-Did you actually try and scare
us straight?

12:10.625 --> 12:13.333
[Girls laugh]
-Yeah.

12:13.375 --> 12:15.500
-I told you this wouldn't work.

12:15.542 --> 12:17.417
